high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the stove.
Pick both pots up from the stove top.
Turn around and go to the sink and stand in front of it.
Put the pots in the sink, turn the water on and then off and take the pots out of the sink.
Go to the right and stand in front of the stove.
Put the pan with the long handle on the bottom, left burner.
anns.task_desc: Remove two pots from the stove to put one back clean.

high_descs: Walk past the fridge on the left to the stove.
Pick up the dirty pot and dirty pan on the stove.
Take the dirty pot and pan to the sink.
Wash the dirty pot and pan in the sink.
Take the clean pot and pan out of the sink and walk back to the stove.
Set the clean pan down on the front left burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Set a clean pan on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and then walk forward and then turn left into the kitchen and then walk to the oven.
Pick up the pot and the pan from the stove.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Rinse the pot and pan in the sink and then pick them back up.
Turn right and walk back to the stove.
Place the pan on the left most burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean pan on the stove while carrying a clean pot.
